========================================================================================================================================================================================================================


to start the recon ng tool in linux = recon-ng
using the -w cmd then the workspaces name it take you directly to the particular workspaces( recon-ng -w example_name )
=========================================================================================================================================================================================================================
workspaces are the seprate folders like structure it can help the user to work on the different work at seprate work spaces 
workspaces cmd  workspaces <create|list|load|remove> these are the basic cmd in workspaces 
CREATE = is used to create a new new workspace
LIST = is used to list the created workspaces 
LOAD = it is use to chage the directry of the workspaces
REMOVE = is used to delete the workspaces
